data.description: OUTSTANDING CURB APPEAL ON THIS 1/2 ACRE NORTHWEST RANCH HOME.  SO MUCH TO OFFER ON THIS SPECTACULAR HOME.  LARGE OPEN FLOORPLAN INCLUDES, 3 LARGE BEDROOMS, MASTER SEPERATE WITH A OFFICE/DEN WITH ALL BUILTIN CABINETS AND STORAGE.  NEWER AC UNITS, PAINT EXTERIOR, HOT WATER HEATER, TOILETS.  MASTER BATH COMPLETELY REMODELED.  MASTER CLOSET CUSTOM WITH BUILTINS.   RING CAMERAS AND LIGHTS INCLUDED.  SURROUND SOUND WITH SPEAKERS INTERIOR AND EXTERIOR.  A BEAUTIFUL KOI POND WITH $4K IN KOI FISH.  AMAZING CUSTOM TUFF SHED IN BACK COMPLETELY FINISHED ON THE INTERIOR FOR OFFICE, OR MAN CAVE OR SHE SHED WITH POWER AND AC.  A BACK YARD OASIS FEATURES MATURE LANDSCAPING FRONT AND BACK.  MULTIPLE FRUIT TREES, APPLE, APRICOT, POMEGRANITE,LEMON PLUM, BLACKBERRY AND GREEN GRAPE VINES.  MULTIPLE MATURE TREES AND ROSE BUSHES FRONT AND BACK. FOR THE EQUESTRIAN TO STALLS WITH TURNOUT AND TACK AND FEED ROOMS.  SO MUCH MORE TO THIS GREAT HOME. THE BEST IS SOLAR PANELS INCLUDED OWNED FREE AND CLEAR!
